Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Gorbachev's Yeltsin rally ban
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yh5pq
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 29 Mar 1991
Gorbachev's banning of a Yeltsin rally in Moscow worries Alistair Cooke before he reflects on a rift between President Bush and General Schwarzkopf.